  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      R(+)pramipexole is administered in escalating doses to patients with early ALS. Plasma and
      spinal fluid levels of R(+)PPX are monitored, in addition to biochemical markers of oxidative
      stress.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
